1
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:44,300
"Unfold"

2
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:47,500
(Episode 6)

3
00:01:57,041 --> 00:01:58,041
Bai Che.

4
00:02:02,833 --> 00:02:04,041
I killed your father.

5
00:02:05,208 --> 00:02:06,208
That kid...

6
00:02:06,875 --> 00:02:08,875
He wants to sell the port
the moment he gets back.

7
00:02:09,375 --> 00:02:10,499
If we hadn't

8
00:02:10,500 --> 00:02:12,260
built this empire with
his father back then,

9
00:02:12,291 --> 00:02:14,250
who does he think he is?

10
00:02:16,666 --> 00:02:19,290
By the way, the organ trafficking

11
00:02:19,291 --> 00:02:21,375
is being cracked down on so hard lately.

12
00:02:22,458 --> 00:02:24,208
It must be that kid's doing.

13
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:26,750
Since we can't make any money,

14
00:02:27,541 --> 00:02:29,541
we won't let him have it easy either.

15
00:02:29,791 --> 00:02:30,958
Next Tuesday,

16
00:02:31,291 --> 00:02:33,583
take a few capable men with you.

17
00:02:34,750 --> 00:02:35,750
Right.

18
00:02:35,875 --> 00:02:37,208
Jufu Farm.

19
00:02:38,250 --> 00:02:40,125
I'm going to ruin that kid.

20
00:02:50,416 --> 00:02:51,416
You're here.

21
00:02:56,875 --> 00:02:57,875
Next Tuesday,

22
00:02:58,083 --> 00:02:59,083
You...

23
00:02:59,250 --> 00:03:01,375
bring Zhao Lingye to Jufu Farm.

24
00:03:04,541 --> 00:03:06,083
He'll never listen to me.

25
00:03:14,416 --> 00:03:16,833
Don't fucking look at me like that.

26
00:03:18,041 --> 00:03:19,041
If it weren't for me,

27
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:22,083
would your mother have found
a matching kidney so quickly?

28
00:03:23,666 --> 00:03:24,750
It's a pity, though.

29
00:03:25,083 --> 00:03:26,083
She was too weak.

30
00:03:27,416 --> 00:03:28,875
Not long after the transplant,

31
00:03:28,958 --> 00:03:29,958
she still didn't make it.

32
00:03:31,708 --> 00:03:33,416
You owe me this.

33
00:03:37,625 --> 00:03:38,625
Uncle Bai,

34
00:03:39,291 --> 00:03:41,375
you said this kidney was worth 700,000.

35
00:03:42,458 --> 00:03:44,416
But the documents Mr. Zhao showed me

36
00:03:44,833 --> 00:03:46,208
say otherwise.

37
00:03:48,083 --> 00:03:49,083
That kidney...

38
00:03:49,250 --> 00:03:51,875
you harvested it from
a lung cancer patient.

39
00:03:59,500 --> 00:04:00,000
I...

40
00:04:00,291 --> 00:04:02,250
I really thought you were helping me.

41
00:04:04,208 --> 00:04:05,583
It was an accident.

42
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,166
Who could have known?

43
00:04:09,291 --> 00:04:11,083
Now go and get it done.

44
00:04:48,458 --> 00:04:49,778
I don't owe you anything anymore.

45
00:05:12,166 --> 00:05:13,500
Bai Ronghui got what he deserved.

46
00:05:14,541 --> 00:05:15,833
He killed my mother,

47
00:05:16,333 --> 00:05:17,333
and he lied to me.

48
00:05:19,166 --> 00:05:20,915
Even you, his so-called son,

49
00:05:20,916 --> 00:05:22,083
was just a lie.

50
00:05:25,666 --> 00:05:26,915
I killed him.

51
00:05:26,916 --> 00:05:28,833
Consider your vengeance avenged too.

52
00:05:29,875 --> 00:05:31,041
You don't have to thank me.

53
00:05:33,583 --> 00:05:35,208
He stole my life.

54
00:05:40,375 --> 00:05:41,375
But...

55
00:05:43,166 --> 00:05:45,125
if you dare get in my way,

56
00:05:45,833 --> 00:05:47,375
I won't be so polite next time.

57
00:05:59,041 --> 00:06:00,041
My card.

58
00:06:00,125 --> 00:06:01,416
In case you lost the other one.

59
00:06:34,625 --> 00:06:36,083
Why didn't you call me?

60
00:06:41,916 --> 00:06:42,916
Let's go.

61
00:07:01,458 --> 00:07:02,698
How long have you been waiting?

62
00:07:05,041 --> 00:07:06,875
What if I hadn't come back today?

63
00:07:14,625 --> 00:07:15,625
Bai Che,

64
00:07:16,625 --> 00:07:17,666
You coming to find me...

65
00:07:17,833 --> 00:07:18,833
makes me very happy.

66
00:07:27,541 --> 00:07:28,625
But next time,

67
00:07:29,250 --> 00:07:30,250
call me.

68
00:07:30,583 --> 00:07:31,583
I'll come pick you up.

69
00:07:37,250 --> 00:07:38,250
Does it hurt?

70
00:07:40,291 --> 00:07:41,291
No.

71
00:07:42,125 --> 00:07:43,125
Liar.

72
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:22,916
What's wrong?

73
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,000
Nothing.

74
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:27,708
You have something to tell me.

75
00:08:29,791 --> 00:08:31,458
Are you leaving here later?

76
00:08:35,527 --> 00:08:37,583
I'll leave once the money
from the port comes in.

77
00:08:41,375 --> 00:08:42,458
I was wondering...

78
00:08:43,333 --> 00:08:44,958
if you would leave me behind.

79
00:08:46,708 --> 00:08:48,166
Why would you think that?

80
00:08:49,541 --> 00:08:51,333
Because I'm one of Lao Bai's people.

81
00:08:53,833 --> 00:08:54,833
Are you?

82
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:57,000
What?

83
00:08:58,958 --> 00:09:00,125
Lao Bai's person?

84
00:09:07,666 --> 00:09:08,666
What do you think?

85
00:09:13,291 --> 00:09:14,750
I don't like guessing.

86
00:09:19,125 --> 00:09:20,125
Cheng Fan,

87
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,333
did you kill Lao Bai

88
00:09:24,333 --> 00:09:25,500
for me,

89
00:09:26,291 --> 00:09:27,583
or for yourself?

90
00:09:35,750 --> 00:09:36,750
Both.

91
00:09:37,791 --> 00:09:38,791
Both?

92
00:09:39,958 --> 00:09:40,958
Which one more?

93
00:09:43,583 --> 00:09:45,103
He wanted me to bring you to the farm.

94
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,333
They were going to hurt you.

95
00:09:47,708 --> 00:09:48,958
So you killed him.

96
00:09:51,833 --> 00:09:52,833
I'm sorry.

97
00:09:59,916 --> 00:10:00,916
After what he did to you,

98
00:10:01,583 --> 00:10:02,666
he deserved to die.

99
00:10:15,291 --> 00:10:16,582
Do you want to take

100
00:10:16,583 --> 00:10:18,000
a plane or a boat?

101
00:10:32,583 --> 00:10:33,903
There's still food in the fridge.

102
00:10:34,041 --> 00:10:35,166
Should I make you something?

103
00:10:49,666 --> 00:10:51,000
How about a drink?

104
00:10:52,958 --> 00:10:54,833
The bottle you had last time is still here.

105
00:10:56,208 --> 00:10:57,166
I even bought

106
00:10:57,167 --> 00:10:58,708
the one you poured for me at the bar.

107
00:11:23,708 --> 00:11:24,708
It's okay.

108
00:11:32,125 --> 00:11:33,125
Zhou Chen...

109
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,875
Why are you so good to me?

110
00:11:45,208 --> 00:11:46,500
Do you really not know?

111
00:12:06,625 --> 00:12:07,833
Can you feel it?

112
00:12:08,833 --> 00:12:10,125
Every time it sees you,

113
00:12:11,208 --> 00:12:12,708
it beats a little faster.

114
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,000
I'm sorry.

115
00:12:25,708 --> 00:12:26,208
I...

116
00:12:26,666 --> 00:12:27,666
It's okay.

117
00:12:28,625 --> 00:12:29,666
We can take it slow.

118
00:14:07,416 --> 00:14:08,416
Zhou Chen,

119
00:14:09,750 --> 00:14:10,750
don't leave me.

120
00:14:11,875 --> 00:14:12,875
I won't.

121
00:14:13,291 --> 00:14:14,291
Never.

